short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Show the relation between likes and total views on a youtube video

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Adds the percentage of views that liked the video.

Examples:

A video with 100 views and 50 likes will show: 50 likes (50%)
A video with 100 views and 1 like will show: 1 like (1%)
